{"tid":575872,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員巴打會唔會揀延遲退休5年?","createTime":"2018-02-28T12:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T13:50:36.000Z","uid":60910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb6a9503cc1f598d41922eb6b930e9b97820c15","tid":575872,"uid":60910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"2015年6月1日前入公務員可以選擇延遲退休5年<br />\n文職65歲﹐紀律部隊60歲<br />\n如果揀延遲5年就要轉新mpf供款比率<br />\n<br />\n如果揀左延遲5年﹐但係到60歲又唔想撈就會蝕mpf<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過而家距離退休仲有好耐<br />\n又唔知到時咩環境<br />\n唔夠錢生活可能都要繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實都幾難揀<br />\n15年6月1日前入職嘅公務員巴打會點揀?"},{"pid":"f98d42ed08f31be6e90a670c8bfcb74a7bb5b3fa","tid":575872,"uid":19062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"比你仲到60歲都老seafood<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番工都係鳩fingfing"},{"pid":"e7369129b0eed6f6335529a1b39051e676bde190","tid":575872,"uid":3122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:11:27.000Z","msg":"緊係會<br />\n最高人工5年<br />\n你話你發左達當然唔洗<br />\n再講MPF都係5%內"},{"pid":"836aa0d9b4d90898f966c06abb3786ac6bd8532e","tid":575872,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:12:26.000Z","msg":"好撚憎返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話捱多5年...<br />\n但又怕到時無錢..."},{"pid":"aa2218dd994c1bfe198dc4760636f7a58e921739","tid":575872,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f98d42ed08f31be6e90a670c8bfcb74a7bb5b3fa","tid":575872,"uid":19062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"比你仲到60歲都老seafood<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番工都係鳩fingfing"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"玩鳩啲後輩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寓工作於娛樂 <img src=\"/asse